channel.title: For everyone thats having problems with moparscape!
channel.description:
ok this should help but IF THIS DOESN'T WORK THE CLIENT WILL FIX ITSELF [ usually takes about 2 days ]
ok heres what u do
-CLICK START AND RIGHT CLICK ON THE INTERNET -CLICK INTERNET PROPERTIES - THEN AT THE TOP CLICK PROGRAMS - THEN CLICK MANAGE ADD - ONS - IT SHOULD SHOW A LIST OF ENABLED/DISABLED DOWNLOADS -ENABLE ALL YOUR JAVA AND SUNTIME PROGRAMS -THEN RESTART YOUR COMPUTER AND TRY IT AGAIN
remember if it doesnt work just wait 2 days
